What you need to know:  Patel won the KNRC title and came within winning ARC Crown which was claimed by Leroy Gomes of ZambiaThe Kenya Motor Sports Federation, which runs all types of motorsports activities in Kenya, held a colourful prize-giving ceremony on Saturday evening at its headquarters at the Kasarani StadiumAnwar Sidi was awarded a Special Award for his continuation as one of the leading Motorsports Photographers across the nation